Step 5: ğŸ“‹ Create Clear Instructions
"How does each person know what to do?"
The Recipe Card Method:
Give each team member a "recipe card" with:
ğŸ‘¤ TEAM MEMBER: [Name]
ğŸ¯ YOUR MISSION: [What they're building]
ğŸ“ YOUR TASKS:
   â–¡ Task 1: [Specific action]
